Vanilla Worksheet Builder: Todo List

1. HTML
   - Create index.html with:
     - Header (logo, title, burger menu)
     - Top action bar (New, Load, Save, Print, PDF, More)
     - Pastel toolbar (empty)
     - Page preview area (A4 aspect ratio, supports multiple pages)
     - "+ Add New Page" text/button
     - (Optional) Modal for worksheet manager

2. CSS
   - Copy all relevant styles from React App.css into a new style.css
   - Link style.css in index.html

3. JavaScript
   - Add page management:
     - Store pages in an array
     - Render all pages in the preview area
     - Implement "+ Add New Page" to add a new page and re-render
   - Top action bar:
     - Hook up "Load" and "Save" to open worksheet manager (modal or new window)
   - Modal logic (optional):
     - Show/hide modal for worksheet manager
     - Pass mode (save/load) to modal
   - Burger menu dropdown logic (optional)
     - Integrate shared burger menu component by invoking insertBurgerMenu('#burger-menu-mount') in main.js
     - Ensure toggle button appears and toggles menu visibility correctly with proper CSS positioning and z-index

4. Worksheet Manager
   - Reuse/adapt your existing worksheet manager HTML/JS for modal or new window

5. Testing
   - Ensure adding pages, opening modals, and all UI elements work as expected
   - Check responsiveness and print preview
